complete the figure by fixing the serpent to a cross?  First he set up
the wood and fixed it in the earth as a post:  then by putting the
brazen serpent athwart (<span class="Greek"><span
id="ii.xvii-p116.2"></span>πλαγίως</span>, he formed a figure of the
Cross.”  Cf. Barnab. *Epist*. c. xii.; Justin M. (*Apol*. i. c. 60);
Iren. (*Hæres.* IV. c. 2); Tertull. *adv. Judæos*, c. 10).

